room_title: Escape room "Dreamscape" by ArtHatch Escape in San Marcos (CA)
room_address: 201 E Grand Ave, Ste 2G, Escondido CA 92025
room_description: You are a part of the Senior class of Dreamwalkers facing their final year’s test at “Onirik: School of Crypto-Dream Exploits”. This dangerous test requires your group to enter “Somnia Orbis” (the Dream World), and decipher the meaning of a young girl’s dream in order to stop it from becoming a nightmare! If you fail, you could be trapped in limbo forever. If there was ever a time to panic, it’s now!
